ender will find it automatically.\n    plan: free # Specifies the free instance type\n    envVars:\n      - key: NODE_ENV\n        value: production\n      - key: DATABASE_URL\n        fromDatabase:\n          name: food-truck-db\n          property: connectionString\n      - key: REDIS_URL\n        fromService:\n          type: redis\n          name: food-truck-redis\n          property: connectionString\n      # IMPORTANT: Secrets like JWT_SECRET are added in the Render dashboard.\n      - key: JWT_SECRET\n        sync: false # This value is managed in the Render dashboard\n\n  # -----------------\n  # Redis Cache\n  # -----------------\n  - type: redis\n    name: food-truck-redis\n    plan: free\n\ndatabases:\n  # -----------------\n  # PostgreSQL Database\n  # -----------------\n  - name: food-truck-db\n    plan: free","telemetry":{"CommentLines":null},"codeBlockIndex":0,"language":"yaml","checkpointFile":"933ff8422f8bc61e1ab20d6b5ad2f7bd16a7f3595271bd66bfc443e978259dce","accepted":true}]},"fileUsage":{"includedFiles":["/home/perrymckay1/render.yaml","/home/perrymckay1/Dockerfile","/home/perrymckay1/node_modules/cors/README.md","/home/perrymckay1/.cache/typescript/5.9/node_modules/@types/node/diagnostics_channel.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/node_modules/@types/node/diagnostics_channel.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/.cache/typescript/5.9/node_modules/@aws-sdk/client-s3/dist-types/commands/PutBucketTaggingCommand.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/node_modules/@aws-sdk/client-s3/dist-types/commands/PutBucketTaggingCommand.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/node_modules/@types/node/timers.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/.cache/typescript/5.9/node_modules/@types/node/timers.d.ts","/home/perrymckay1/.cache/typescript/5.9/node_modules/csstype/README.md","/home/perrymckay1/.cache/typescript/5.9/node_modules/delayed-stream/Readme.md","/home/perrymckay1/node_modules/@aws-sdk/nested-clients/dist-types/submodules/sso/index.d.ts"]},"suggestedPrompts":["How do I generate a strong, secure JWT_SECRET?","How do I 